Scaleway SDK
============

This package provides tools to query the REST APIs of `Scaleway`_.

.. image:: https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/scaleway-sdk.svg?style=flat
    :target: https://pypi.python.org/pypi/scaleway-sdk
    :alt: Last release
